messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Enemy communication intercepted. Security level elevated.

A summary has been copied and printed to all communications consoles.

messages.author: Head of Security's Desk
messages.body: The clown has already attacked me and stolen my gun, he is to be arrested on sight

messages.author: Head of Security's Desk
messages.body: I have the clowns PDA and bannana back, if i don't get my back soon the clown will be KoS

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Anomaly Alert

Localized hyper-energetic flux wave detected on long range scanners. Expected location: Medbay Central.

messages.author: Head of Security's Desk
messages.body: I feel liek i have done the bulk of my work, i am going SSD forever
